# repclaw Demo — terminal chat client for OpenClaw
# Record with: vhs demo.tape

Output docs/demo.gif
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 960
Set Height 540
Set Padding 10
Set TypingSpeed 50ms

# Launch repclaw
Type "repclaw"
Sleep 1s
Enter
Sleep 3s

# Agent list loads — select the main agent (first in list)
Enter
Sleep 2s

# First message: something fun and short
Type "Write me a mass limerick about mass cats who write Go code"
Sleep 500ms
Enter

# Wait for the streaming response to complete
Sleep 15s

# Quit
Ctrl+C
Sleep 1s
